==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*'''[[color by numbers]]'''

===Noun===
'''[[color]] [[by]] [[number]]'''

# {{cattag|usually used attributively}} A simple drawing exercise, intended especially for children, consisting of a line drawing that divides the artwork into distinct spaces, the indended color of each indicated by a number and referenced from a key.
# {{uncountable}} A technique the applies such exercises, as used until recently in the production of large-scale animations for instance.

===Verb===
''to'' '''[[color]] [[by]] [[number]]'''

# To complete such an exercise; to carry out such a technique by filling in each space with the appropriate color.